snippet.title: Skyseeker Open Beta Trailer
snippet.description:
Enter a world where ancient creatures thrive in freezing glaciers, boiling rivers, and enormous oceans of fog. As a Skyseeker, join the legendary explorers who tame these monsters and attempt to reach the summit of the sky, in a grand monster-collecting metroidvania adventure.

Play Beta: https://kvfrans.itch.io/skyseeker
Wishlist us on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1372820/Skyseeker/
Join us on Discord: https://discord.gg/jkY97xH
